  "body": "#### System information\n\nGeth version: `1.3.0` - `1.4.7`, `develop`\nOS & Version: Linux & OSX\n#### Expected behaviour\n\nNo crash, no RPC timeouts\n#### Actual behaviour\n\ngeth crashes\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\nAdding and deleting filters in fast succession.\n#### Backtrace\n\nThis is a `1.4.6` backtrace. The race was recreated for the same results in `1.3.6`, `1.4.4` and `1.4.7` and code compared with all `1.3.x`, `1.4.x` and `develop`.\n\n```\nfatal error: concurrent map read and map write\n\ngoroutine 17456 [running]:\nruntime.throw(0x1131ba0, 0x21)\n        /tmp/go/src/runtime/panic.go:547 +0x90 fp=0xc838a00f80 sp=0xc838a00f68\nruntime.mapaccess2_faststr(0xcedae0, 0xc820430390, 0xc83a9ee060, 0x22, 0x0, 0x428fd7)\n        /tmp/go/src/runtime/hashmap_fast.go:307 +0x5b fp=0xc838a00fe0 sp=0xc838a00f80\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth/filters.(*PublicFilterAPI).GetFilterLogs(0xc821af0000, 0xc83a9ee060, 0x22, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\n        /tmp/go-ethereum/build/_workspace/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth/filters/api.go:528 +0x6d fp=0xc838a01048 sp=0xc838a00fe0\nruntime.call64(0xc8221a3000, 0xfab5c8, 0xc83a9ee0c0, 0x1800000030)\n        /tmp/go/src/runtime/asm_amd64.s:473 +0x3e fp=0xc838a01090 sp=0xc838a01048\nreflect.Value.call(0xdc3520, 0xfab5c8, 0x13, 0xffb310, 0x4, 0xc83a9ee090, 0x2, 0x2, 0x0, 0x0, ...)\n        /tmp/go/src/reflect/value.go:435 +0x120d fp=0xc838a013e0 sp=0xc838a01090\nreflect.Value.Call(0xdc3520, 0xfab5c8, 0x13, 0xc83a9ee090, 0x2, 0x2, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\n        /tmp/go/src/reflect/value.go:303 +0xb1 fp=0xc838a01440 sp=0xc838a013e0\n```\n",
